hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: perfect design thanks cipralex generico prezzo We discovered the whole alphabet while packing for our longed-for trip to Puglia, on the south-eastern coast of Italy. This, we had promised ourselves, would be a richly deserved, sun-filled five-day escape from the dark, dank winter that was all Hugh had ever really known. We laughed at how he would be surprised and delighted by the phenomenon of sunshine. We smiled in anticipation of his joy at not having to be swaddled in endless layers before every excursion outside. How odd it would be for him, we mused, not to hear Daddy utter unspeakable oaths through gritted teeth while forcing tiny infant legs into multiple pairs of tiny woollen tights. Aaahhhh.
